msgctxt "GameRomHorse00L_Name"
msgid "Giant Horse"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GameRomHorse00L_PictureBook"
msgid ""
"This giant horse is the last of its kind. Its\n"
"physical capabilities completely overshadow\n"
"those of regular horses, but its temperament\n"
"is extremely wild. Only a truly skilled rider can\n"
"train, or even catch, this beast of a mount.\n"
"This is a horse that chooses its rider."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GameRomHorse00S_Name"
msgid "Donkey"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GameRomHorse00S_PictureBook"
msgid ""
"Smaller than horses, these are raised as\n"
"livestock in the countryside, so they don't\n"
"exist in the wild. They're more powerful\n"
"than they look and specialize in transporting\n"
"baggage. This has made them popular with\n"
"traveling merchants."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GameRomHorseBone_Name"
msgid "Stalhorse"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GameRomHorseBone_PictureBook"
msgid ""
"This skeletal horse is ridden by monsters.\n"
"It was once a regular horse, but Ganon's\n"
"power revived it from death. It cannot\n"
"maintain its bone structure in the daytime."
msgstr ""

